active_listings.description: Beautifully restored Victorian home in historic downtown. Features original hardwood floors, stained glass windows, and modern updates throughout. Walking distance to Mission Inn and downtown amenities.
Stunning contemporary home in sought-after Woodcrest neighborhood. Open floor plan with gourmet kitchen, master suite with spa-like bathroom, and backyard oasis with pool.
Luxurious Mediterranean estate with breathtaking mountain views. Features include chef's kitchen, home theater, wine cellar, and resort-style backyard with infinity pool.
Modern townhouse with low maintenance lifestyle. Features include attached garage, private patio, and community amenities. Perfect for first-time buyers or investors.
Beautiful traditional home in growing La Sierra area. Features include formal dining room, family room with fireplace, and large backyard perfect for entertaining.
Modern urban loft in the heart of downtown. High ceilings, exposed brick, and floor-to-ceiling windows. Walk to restaurants, shops, and entertainment.
Charming Craftsman home with covered front porch. Features include built-in cabinetry, cozy fireplace, and beautifully landscaped backyard.
Stunning modern ranch with panoramic city and mountain views. Open concept living with chef's kitchen, home office, and luxurious primary suite.
Charming Spanish-style townhouse in gated community. Features include tile roof, arched doorways, and private courtyard. Low HOA fees.
Spacious California ranch with open floor plan and indoor-outdoor living. Features include gourmet kitchen, bonus room, and covered patio perfect for entertaining.
Brand new modern condo in downtown's newest building. Features premium finishes, in-unit laundry, and rooftop amenities. Perfect for urban professionals.
Elegant traditional estate on premium lot. Features include formal living and dining, spacious bedrooms, game room, and resort-style backyard with pool and spa.
Magnificent Spanish Colonial masterpiece with sweeping valley views. Features include grand entry, gourmet kitchen, theater room, wine cellar, and casita.
Beautifully updated mid-century modern home with original character intact. Features include vaulted ceilings, terrazzo floors, and wall of windows overlooking private yard.
Contemporary ranch on over an acre of usable land. Features include open concept living, luxurious master retreat, and room for horses/animals. Bring your toys!
Modern townhouse in vibrant downtown location. Features include open living area, private balcony, attached garage, and walking distance to everything.
Charming modern farmhouse with board-and-batten siding and covered porch. Features include shaker cabinetry, farmhouse sink, and spacious backyard.
Sleek contemporary home with clean lines and abundant natural light. Features include chef's kitchen, spa bathroom, and outdoor living with fire pit.
Well-maintained duplex with two 3-bedroom units. Perfect for owner-occupant or investor. Both units feature updated kitchens and separate utilities.
Beautiful Mediterranean home with tile roof and arched details. Features include courtyard entry, gourmet kitchen, and covered loggia overlooking pool.
Charming historic bungalow with period details lovingly preserved. Features include built-ins, original woodwork, and large covered porch. Updated systems.
Brand new transitional home with designer finishes throughout. Features include quartz counters, luxury vinyl plank, and covered California room.
Spectacular contemporary home with walls of glass capturing stunning views. Features include great room, gourmet kitchen, media room, and infinity edge pool.
Stylish modern condo near UCR. Perfect for students, faculty, or investors. Features include stainless appliances, in-unit laundry, and pool/spa access.
Stunning country estate on 2.5 acres with mountain views. Features include wraparound porch, gourmet kitchen, barn, and room for horses. True country living!
Unique industrial loft with exposed ductwork and concrete floors. Features include 14-foot ceilings, floor-to-ceiling windows, and urban lifestyle amenities.
Adorable cottage-style home with charming curb appeal. Features include shiplap accents, vintage fixtures, and cozy outdoor living space. Move-in ready!
Architectural masterpiece with cutting-edge design and smart home technology. Features include elevator, dual master suites, temperature-controlled wine room, and resort backyard.
Well-maintained traditional home in family-friendly neighborhood. Features include spacious kitchen, bonus room, and nicely landscaped backyard with patio.
Beautiful Southwest-style home with stucco exterior and tile roof. Features include great room, chef's kitchen, covered patio, and low-maintenance desert landscaping.
Classic Craftsman with original character and modern updates. Features include built-in bookcases, box beam ceilings, and charming front porch. Walk to everything!
Elegant Colonial with symmetrical facade and columned entry. Features include formal rooms, library, upstairs bonus, and professionally landscaped grounds.
Spectacular Tuscan villa with imported tile and Old World charm. Features include wine cellar, chef's kitchen, loggia, and infinity pool with city views.
Brand new modern townhouse in convenient location. Features include open floor plan, quartz counters, luxury vinyl plank, and attached 2-car garage.
Stunning Prairie-style home with horizontal lines and natural materials. Features include great room, gourmet kitchen, and outdoor living with mountain views.
Unique converted warehouse loft with soaring 18-foot ceilings and original brick. Features include industrial kitchen, mezzanine office, and private balcony.
Charming French Country estate with stone and stucco exterior. Features include courtyard entry, gourmet kitchen, study, and pool with outdoor kitchen.
Breathtaking contemporary masterpiece with stunning architecture. Features include floating staircase, chef's kitchen, spa bathroom, and negative edge pool.
Charming vintage bungalow with loads of character. Features include arched doorways, original hardwood, built-ins, and updated kitchen and baths.
Beautiful modern farmhouse with board-and-batten siding and metal roof. Features include shiplap walls, barn doors, farmhouse sink, and covered patio.
Versatile live/work loft in arts district. Features include 12-foot ceilings, polished concrete, flex space, and rooftop deck with city views.
Classic Cape Cod with dormers and shutters. Features include formal dining, family room with fireplace, and beautifully maintained yard with mature trees.
Exquisite Italian villa on one acre with breathtaking views. Features include grand entry, library, theater, gym, wine cellar, and resort-style pool.
Ground-floor garden-style condo with private patio. Features include updated kitchen, walk-in closet, and resort-style amenities. Great investment!
Stunning rustic contemporary with wood and stone accents. Features include vaulted great room, gourmet kitchen, spa master, and outdoor living with views.
Spectacular top-floor penthouse with 360-degree views. Features include floor-to-ceiling glass, chef's kitchen, spa baths, and private rooftop terrace.
Charming Tudor with half-timbering and brick facade. Features include arched doorways, leaded glass windows, library with built-ins, and English garden.
Stunning Northwest contemporary with natural materials and indoor-outdoor flow. Features include great room, chef's kitchen, wine cellar, and covered outdoor living.
Beautifully preserved California bungalow with original charm. Features include period fixtures, built-in hutch, coved ceilings, and updated kitchen/baths.
Magnificent equestrian estate on 5 pristine acres. Features include luxury main house, 6-stall barn, arena, guest house, pool, and panoramic mountain views.
